gmnotes.label: GM Notes
gmnotes.value: Max is a drunken scruff of a Highwayman, who won’t listen to anyone about the big mistake he’s making. He is of average height and light build, with prominent cheekbones. His hair is black, and falls over his eyes in a messy fringe. He wears elaborate military dress uniform under his cape, but it has become rather threadbare and tatty. He also wears ill-fitting boots and a slightly tragic bicorn hat.
